":849820,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62f71a18e1fe8e2c1a5eed7a176238c319ef27d","tid":849820,"uid":39216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:17:31.000Z","msg":"我想聽講座呀，唔係講咗呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"跟住再問有冇出路，真係笑到嘔泡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9485525e8c2209668cc4b1aa5b361788b89b1abf","tid":849820,"uid":85284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"好懷念當年嘅電台節目<br />\n無論係 DJ 抑或 節目質素<br />\n同而家嗰啲比真係差天共地"},{"pid":"428e4200e8c07d0d9e28706a6fb9d242209a9b44","tid":849820,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"牛餐肉，上壯瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822ba58aafa43134c5c3d6cc44fd5732efccd4dd","tid":849820,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"Yes個個眾裡尋他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7998dfe09d487d64f9060b85ed816dc7050dfb","tid":849820,"uid":31963,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"的確呢度小朋友太多，佢地唔會明白七十後晌未有互聯網嘅時代，娛樂係幾咁難搵到&hellip; 你估好似而家嗰d 濕鳩youtuber 亂鳩拍片就係娛樂呀?"},{"pid":"31dba27d75ba4ed80853128d6660d83348b98e03","tid":849820,"uid":3112,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"依家d 00後剩係識get到支那式幽默<br />\n傳統港式幽默係佢地眼中變左係無聊同on9既代名詞<br />\n佢地應該未經歷過連smartphone都冇，搵娛樂就要聽電台睇雜誌既時代<br />\n仲記得當年一上網就打唔到電話，仲要好撚貴"},{"p